A Study on the Application Strategies of Railway Freight Big Data
LI Bin (Freight Department, China Railway Zhengzhou Group Co., Ltd., Zhengzhou 450052, Henan, China)
Abstract: Railway freight big data, as an essential railway information asset, is characterized by multiple types, fast growth, and high accuracy, which has great development potential and application value. Based on an analysis of the characteristics of the railway freight big data, to address the inadequacy problems in the aspects of internal data sharing, external data fusion, and data analysis capability, this paper puts forward the strategies in terms of freight production, operation control, and safety management, which are expected to promote railway freight production and improve operation and safety management. Keywords: Railway Freight Transportation; Big Data; Freight Production; Operation Control; Safety Management; Application Strategies
